import * as React from "react"

function Device() {
    return (
        <svg
          width={313}
          height={485}
          viewBox="0 0 313 485"
          fill="none"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          xmlnsXlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
         
        >
          <path fill="#fff" d="M0 .78h313V485H0z" />
          <path fill="url(#prefix__pattern0)" d="M0 .779h313V485H0z" />
          <defs>
            <pattern
              id="prefix__pattern0"
              patternContentUnits="objectBoundingBox"
              width={1}
              height={1}
            >
              <use
                xlinkHref="#prefix__image0"
                transform="matrix(.00174 0 0 .00114 0 .008)"
              />
            </pattern>
            <image
              id="prefix__image0"
              width={576}
              height={1280}
              xlinkHref="data:image/jpeg;base64,"
            />
          </defs>
        </svg>
      )
}

export default Device
